### Clinical Resources:  
* [GTRx](https://gtrx.radygenomiclab.com/?m=conditions)  
* [Physicianâ€™s Guide to the Laboratory Diagnosis of Metabolic Diseases](pdf/Blau.pdf)  
* [Metabolic, Nutritional, Iatrogenic, and Artifactual Sources of Urinary Organic Acids: A Comprehensive Table](pdf/OA.pdf)  
* [Nutrition Management of Inherited Metabolic Diseases](pdf/Nutrition.pdf)  

### Smorgasbord (i.e. collection of miscellaneous tools):  
* [PhenoTips](https://phenotips.com/index.html)  
* [HGNC](https://www.genenames.org/)  

### Phenotype to Genotype (i.e. pre-sequencing):  
* [AMELIE](https://amelie.stanford.edu/)  
* [Phenomizer](https://compbio.charite.de/phenomizer/)  
* [GDDP](https://gddp.research.cchmc.org/)  
* [VIBE](https://vibe.molgeniscloud.org/)  
* [GADO](https://www.genenetwork.nl/gado)  
* [PubCaseFinder](https://pubcasefinder.dbcls.jp/)  

### Genotype to Phenotype (i.e. post-sequencing):  
[12 Question to Always Ask a Variant](http://publish.illinois.edu/compgenomicscourse/files/2021/06/Clinical-Variant-Interpretation_Morales-Rosado_2021.pdf)

* Common or rare?
  + [gnomAD](https://gnomad.broadinstitute.org/)  
  + [Frequency Filter](http://cardiodb.org/allelefrequencyapp/)  
  + [MARRVEL](http://marrvel.org/)  
* Variant Impact/Type
  + [Ensembl Variant Effect Predictor](https://useast.ensembl.org/info/docs/tools/vep/index.html)
  + [InterVar](https://wintervar.wglab.org/)
  + [ClinGen Dosage Sensitivity](https://clinicalgenome.org/curation-activities/dosage-sensitivity/)
  + [Varsome](https://varsome.com/)
  + [Franklin](https://franklin.genoox.com/clinical-db/home)
  + [GeneScout](https://genescout.omim.org/)
* Linkage to Disease Causing Variant?
  + [TopLD](http://topld.genetics.unc.edu/)
* In-silico predictions?
  + Splicing:
      + [SpliceAI](https://spliceailookup.broadinstitute.org/)
      + [Human Splicing Finder](https://www.genomnis.com/access-hsf)
  + microRNA Regulation:
      + [dbMTS](http://database.liulab.science/dbMTS)
  + Variant functional prediction:
      + [PredictSNP](https://loschmidt.chemi.muni.cz/predictsnp/)
      + [CAPICE](https://capice.molgeniscloud.org/)
      + [dbNSFP](http://database.liulab.science/dbNSFP)
          + [An expanded phenotype centric benchmark of variant prioritization tools](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC9313608/)
* Constraint metrics
  + [gnomAD](https://gnomad.broadinstitute.org/help/constraint)
      + [A map of constrained coding regions in the human genome](https://www.nature.com/articles/s41588-018-0294-6)
      + [The mutational constraint spectrum quantified from variation in 141,456 humans](https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2308-7)
* Residue/Domain? Hotspot?
  + [UniProtKB](https://www.uniprot.org/help/uniprotkb)
  + [InterPro](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/interpro/)
  + [PDBe](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/pdbe/entry/search/index/?advancedSearch:true=)
  + [reactome](https://reactome.org/)
  + [AlphaFold](https://alphafold.ebi.ac.uk/entry/P31271)
* Variant effect functionally studied?
  + [PubMed](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/advanced/)
  + [LitSense](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/research/litsense/)
* Interpretation Databases
  + [ClinVar](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/clinvar/)
  + [HGMD](https://www.hgmd.cf.ac.uk/ac/index.php)
  + [UCSC genome browser](https://genome.ucsc.edu/cgi-bin/hgGateway)
  + [ANNOVAR](https://wannovar.wglab.org/)
  + [DECIPHER](https://www.deciphergenomics.org/ddd/overview)
* Previously reported cases?
  + [HPO](https://hpo.jax.org/app/)
  + [OLIDA: Oligogenic Diseases Database](https://olida.ibsquare.be/)
  + [OMIM](https://www.omim.org/)
  + [GeneReviews](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK1116/advanced/)
  + [FindZebra](https://www.findzebra.com/)
  + [NORD](https://rarediseases.org/advanced-search/)
  + [MedlinePlus](https://medlineplus.gov/about/using/searchtips/)
* Phenotype specificity
* Segregation? De novo?
* Trans/cis observations
  







